Re: Not sure if I got this right...
by Hyperworm » Thu 03.25.2010 10:21 am Well, except that 「ことにしたの？」 isn't a passive construction like "Has... been decided?", but an active construction with a subject, as ThePacster translated it in the first reply to this topic.(AFAIK)
